$Id: README,v 1.3 2002/07/03 11:44:43 terotil Exp $

This is the README-file of ejscc, a program to compile Extended Java
Sketchpad Constructions to ordinary syntax.

Documentation including compile/install instructions and ejsc language
reference can be found from doc/manual.*.


